        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "experience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是经历，一件发生在你身上、后来可以回忆和讲出来的事。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had an amusing experience last year."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以是 funny travel experience，也可以是 school experience，或者 embarrassing experience。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
