      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "language"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "language"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是语言，比如 English、French、Chinese。课文里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he replied in the same language"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是他用同一种语言回答。正是这一点让作者以为自己的法语假设是对的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 381.204,
      "end": 388.868,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是过去故事里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had done"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。先别急着背术语，我们从动作顺序看。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 389.218,
      "end": 402.925,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After I had left a small village, I drove on to the next town."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先离开村庄，后开往下一个镇。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had left"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就像在过去故事里插一块小牌子：这个动作更早发生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 403.275,
      "end": 415.283,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As soon as he had got into the car, I said good morning to him."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先上车，后问好。所以用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had got into the car"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "指更早的动作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 415.633,
      "end": 430.029,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had nearly reached the town, when the young man suddenly said, very slowly, \"Do you speak English?\""
        },
        {
